ope=\"row\"|{{Escyr|2013}}\n|[[Moje 3]]\n|{{flagicon|Sweden}} [[Malm\u00f6]]\n|{{center|<ref name=\"barbara dex\"/>}}\n|}\n\n==Commentators and spokespersons==\nAll the events were broadcast on [[RTS1]], except the {{Escyr|2013}} grand final, the {{Escyr|2015}} second semi-final, which were broadcast on [[RTS2]].\n{|class=\"wikitable sortable plainrowheaders\" style=\"font-size:90%;\"\n|-\n!Year\n!Commentator\n!Spokesperson\n!class=\"unsortable\"|{{Abbr|Ref.|Reference}}\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|{{Escyr|2007}}\n|[[Du\u0161ka Vu\u010dini\u0107-Lu\u010di\u0107]] ||Maja Nikoli\u0107 ||\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|{{Escyr|2008}}\n|[[Dragan Ili\u0107]], Mladen Popovi\u0107 ||[[Du\u0161ica Spasi\u0107]] ||<ref>{{cite web|url=http://blog.b92.net/text/3059/Eurosong%20finale/|title=Eurosong finale|publisher=b92.net|accessdate=2008-05-24}}</ref>\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|{{Escyr|2009}}\n|Dragan Ili\u0107 {{small|(semi-final 1)}}<br>Du\u0161ka Vu\u010dini\u0107-Lu\u010di\u0107 {{small|(semi-final 2, final)}}||[[Jovana Jankovi\u0107]] ||\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|{{Escyr|2010}}\n|Du\u0161ka Vu\u010dini\u0107-Lu\u010di\u0107 {{small|(semi-final 1, final)}}<br>Dragan Ili\u0107 {{small|(semi-final 2)}}||Maja Nikoli\u0107 ||\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|{{Escyr|2011}}\n|Marina Nikoli\u0107 {{small|(semi-final 1)}}<br>Dragan Ili\u0107 {{small|(semi-final 2)}}<br>Du\u0161ka Vu\u010dini\u0107-Lu\u010di\u0107 {{small|(final)}}||Du\u0161ica Spasi\u0107 ||<ref name=\"Pesma Evrovizije 2011\">{{cite web|url=http://www.rts.rs/page/tv/sr/story/20/RTS+1/887122/Pesma+Evrovizije+2011.html|title=Pesma Evrovizije 2011|date=8 May 2011|work=[[Radio Television of Serbia|RTS]]|accessdate=8 May 2011}}</ref>\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|{{Escyr|2012}}\n||Dragan Ili\u0107 {{small|(semi-final 1)}}<br>Du\u0161ka Vu\u010dini\u0107-Lu\u010di\u0107 {{small|(semi-final 2, final)}}|| rowspan=\"2\" |Maja Nikoli\u0107 ||<ref name=\"Serbian broadcast\">{{cite web |url=http://www.rts.rs/page/tv/sr/story/20/RTS+1/1105042/Pesma+Evrovizije+2012.html |title=Pesma Evrovizije 2012 |work=RTS |language=Serbian |date=19 May 2012 |accessdate=19 May 2012 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120521040930/http://www.rts.rs/page/tv/sr/story/20/RTS+1/1105042/Pesma+Evrovizije+2012.html |archive-date=21 May 2012 |url-status=live |df=dmy-all }}</ref>\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|{{Escyr|2013}}\n|Du\u0161ka Vu\u010dini\u0107-Lu\u010di\u0107 {{small|(semi-final 1)}}<br>Marina Nikoli\u0107 {{small|(semi-final 2)}}<br>[[Silvana Gruji\u0107]] {{small|(final)}}||<ref name=SerbCom>{{cite web|author=<!--Staff writer(s); no by-line.-->|script-title=sr:\u041f\u0435\u0441\u043c\u0430 \u0415\u0432\u0440\u043e\u0432\u0438\u0437\u0438\u0458\u0435 2013 \u2013 \u0434\u0440\u0443\u0433\u043e \u043f\u043e\u043b\u0443\u0444\u0438\u043d\u0430\u043b\u0435, \u043f\u0440\u0435\u043d\u043e\u0441|url=http://www.rts.rs/page/tv/ci/story/17/%D0%A0%D0%A2%D0%A1+1/1324362/%D0%9F%D0%B5%D1%81%D0%BC%D0%B0+%D0%95%D0%B2%D1%80%D0%BE%D0%B2%D0%B8%D0%B7%D0%B8%D1%98%D0%B5+2013+-+%D0%B4%D1%80%D1%83%D0%B3%D0%BE+%D0%BF%D0%BE%D0%BB%D1%83%D1%84%D0%B8%D0%BD%D0%B0%D0%BB%D0%B5%2C+%D0%BF%D1%80%D0%B5%D0%BD%D0%BE%D1%81.html|publisher=[[Radio Television of Serbia]]|language=Serbian|trans-title=Eurovision Song Contest 2013 \u2013 first semi-final|date=15 May 2013|accessdate=15 May 2013|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130608055841/http://www.rts.rs/page/tv/ci/story/17/%D0%A0%D0%A2%D0%A1+1/1324362/%D0%9F%D0%B5%D1%81%D0%BC%D0%B0+%D0%95%D0%B2%D1%80%D0%BE%D0%B2%D0%B8%D0%B7%D0%B8%D1%98%D0%B5+2013+-+%D0%B4%D1%80%D1%83%D0%B3%D0%BE+%D0%BF%D0%BE%D0%BB%D1%83%D1%84%D0%B8%D0%BD%D0%B0%D0%BB%D0%B5,+%D0%BF%D1%80%D0%B5%D0%BD%D0%BE%D1%81.html|archive-date=8 June 2013|url-status=live|df=dmy-all}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|author=<!--Staff writer(s); no by-line.-->|script-title=sr:\u0424\u0438\u043d\u0430\u043b\u0435 \u041f\u0435\u0441\u043c\u0435 \u0415\u0432\u0440\u043e\u0432\u0438\u0437\u0438\u0458\u0435 2013|url=http://www.rts.rs/page/tv/ci/story/17/%D0%A0%D0%A2%D0%A1+1/1325794/%D0%A4%D0%B8%D0%BD%D0%B0