ti-TV-airs-the-first-motion-capture-game-show-in-Tamil/articleshow/47498408.cms|title=Chutti TV airs the first motion capture game show in Tamil - Times of India|website=The Times of India|language=en|access-date=2019-08-17}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.deccanchronicle.com/entertainment/kollywood/020619/thirukkural-in-animated-form-a-hit.html|title=Thirukkural in animated form a hit|last=Subramanian|first=Anupama|date=2019-06-02|website=Deccan Chronicle|language=en|access-date=2019-08-17}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.exchange4media.com/media-tv-news/spotlight-is-magic-ingredient-named-innovation-missing-from-kids-content-in-south-india-92624.html|title=Spotlight: Is Magic ingredient named innovation missing from kids content in South India? - Exchange4media|website=Indian Advertising Media & Marketing News \u2013 exchange4media|language=en|access-date=2019-08-17}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.televisionpost.com/sun-tv-acquires-three-animated-series-from-cyber-group-studios-for-chutti-tv/|title=Sun TV acquires three animated series from Cyber Group Studios for Chutti TV - TelevisionPost: Latest News, India\u2019s Television, Cable, DTH, TRAI|date=2018-12-04|website=TelevisionPost: Latest News, India\u2019s Television, Cable, DTH,  TRAI|language=en-US|access-date=2019-08-17}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.indiantelevision.com/television/tv-channels/kids/kids-prefer-home-grown-content-feature-films-on-tv-190319|title=Kids prefer home-grown content, feature films on TV|date=2019-03-19|website=Indian Television Dot Com|language=en|access-date=2019-08-17}}</ref>\n\nChutti TV is a pay channel available on most local cable television networks.  It is also available on [[Astro (television)|ASTRO]] in Malaysia via Channel 213.\n<!-- SOURCE EACH AND EVERY PROGRAMME/NETWORK HERE BEFORE UNHIDING, SEE TALKPAGE -->\n \n==See also==\n* [[Sun Group]]\n* [[Sun TV Network]]\n* [[List of Tamil-language television channels]]\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}