300164/|website=Indian Kanoon|accessdate=11 July 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n| {{flagicon|Indonesia}} [[Indonesia]] || {{no|Illegal}} || Uncertain || {{yes|Legal}} || {{no|Illegal}} || {{no|Illegal}} || {{no|Illegal}} || All forms of pornography are technically illegal, but Indonesia has no laws regarding child pornography online. Indonesia is called a heaven for child pornography.\n|-\n| {{flagicon|Iran}} [[Iran]] || {{no|Illegal}} || {{no|Illegal}} || {{no|Illegal}} || {{no|Illegal}} || {{no|Illegal}} || {{no|Illegal}} || All forms of pornography are illegal.\n|-\n! style=\"width:120px;\"| Country{{refn|name=Real|group=Note}} !! Real child pornography !! Fictional child pornography !! Possession !! Sale !! Production !! Distribution !! Notes\n|-\n| {{flagicon|Israel}} [[Israel]] ''(excluding [[Palestinian territories]])'' || {{no|Illegal}} || {{no|Illegal}} || {{no|Illegal}} || {{no|Illegal}} || {{no|Illegal}} || {{no|Illegal}} ||\n|-\n| {{flagicon|Italy}} [[Italy]] || {{no|Illegal}} || {{no|Illegal}} || {{no|Illegal}} || {{no|Illegal}} || {{no|Illegal}} || {{no|Illegal}} || All forms of child pornography are illegal in accordance with EU law.<ref name=\"citation.allacademic.com\"/>\n|-\n| {{flagicon|Jamaica}} [[Jamaica]] || {{no|Illegal}} || {{no|Illegal}} || {{no|Illegal}} || {{no|Illegal}} || {{no|Illegal}} || {{no|Illegal}} || All forms of pornography are illegal.\n|-\n| {{flagicon|Japan}} [[Japan]] || {{no|Illegal}}<ref>{{cite news|title=Ban on possession of child porn takes effect in Japan|url=http://www.japantimes.co.jp/news/2015/07/15/national/crime-legal/hit-global-criticism-japan-bans-individual-possession-child-porn-images-manga-exempt/#.Vk7h0XLALFb|accessdate=20 November 2015|agency=[[Kyodo News]]|publisher=[[The Japan Times]]|date=15 July 2015}}</ref> || {{yes|Legal}} || {{partial|Legal; fictional only}} || {{partial|Legal; fictional only (unless [[:ja:\u308f\u3044\u305b\u3064\u7269\u9812\u5e03\u7b49\u306e\u7f6a|obscene]])}} || {{partial|Legal; fictional only}} || {{partial|Legal; fictional only (unless [[:ja:\u308f\u3044\u305b\u3064\u7269\u9812\u5e03\u7b49\u306e\u7f6a|obscene]])}} || A law came into effect in 1999 that forbids the sale, production and distribution of child pornography as well as the possession of child pornography for the aforementioned purposes. Simple possession (with no intent to sell, produce, or distribute) was outlawed in 2014; [[Hentai]] was excluded to prevent abuse of the law due to its [[ambiguity]].\n|-\n| {{flagicon|Kazakhstan}} [[Kazakhstan]] || {{no|Illegal}} || {{no|Illegal}} || {{yes|Legal}} || {{no|Illegal}} || {{no|Illegal}} || {{no|Illegal}} ||\n|-\n| {{flagicon|Kenya}} [[Kenya]] || {{no|Illegal}} || {{no|Illegal}} || {{no|Illegal}} || {{no|Illegal}} || {{no|Illegal}} || {{no|Illegal}} || All forms of pornography are illegal.\n|-\n| {{flagicon|Kosovo}} [[Kosovo]] || {{no|Illegal}} || {{no|Illegal}} || {{no|Illegal}} || {{no|Illegal}} || {{no|Illegal}} || {{no|Illegal}} || \n|-\n| {{flagicon|Kuwait}} [[Kuwait]] || {{no|Illegal}} || {{no|Illegal}} || {{no|Illegal}} || {{no|Illegal}} || {{no|Illegal}} || {{no|Illegal}} ||Any kind of pornography is illegal.\n|-\n| {{flagicon|Lesotho}} [[Lesotho]] || {{no|Illegal}} || {{no|Illegal}} || {{no|Illegal}} || {{no|Illegal}} || {{no|Illegal}} || {{no|Illegal}} ||\n|-\n| {{flagicon|Liberia}} [[Liberia]] || {{no|Illegal}} || {{no|Illegal}} || {{no|Illegal}} || {{no|Illegal}} || {{no|Illegal}} || {{no|Illegal}} ||\n|-\n! style=\"width:120px;\"| Country{{refn|name=Real|group=Note}} !! Real child pornography !! Fictional child pornography !! Possession !! Sale !! Production !! Distribution !! Notes\n|-\n| {{flagicon|Libya}} [[Libya]] || {{no|Illegal}} || {{no|Illegal}} || {{no|Illegal}} || {{no|Illegal}} || {{no|Illegal}} || {{no|Illegal}} || All forms of pornography are illegal.\n|-\n| {{flagicon|Macau}} [[Macau]] || {{no|Illegal}} || {{no|Illegal}} || Uncertain || {{no|Illegal}} || {{no|Illegal}} || {{no|Illegal}} ||\n|-\n| {{flagicon|Madagascar}} [[